# nalam.me project context

Static portfolio site. Repo root is the web root; GitHub Pages serves it at `nalam.me`.

## Stack

- HTML: single `index.html` (Start Bootstrap Freelancer 3.3.7 theme)
- CSS: CDN Bootstrap 3 + Freelancer; local `less/` is source-only (not compiled by Gulp)
- JS: jQuery 3, Bootstrap 3, Freelancer theme JS — all from CDN
- Dev: Yarn, Gulp 4, Browser-Sync (port 3000)

## Key files

- `index.html` — all page content, nav, portfolio modals, analytics
- `403.html`, `404.html`, `50x.html` — static error pages
- `CNAME` — custom domain `nalam.me`
- `gulpfile.js` — serves `./`, watches `*.html` and `less/*.less`

## Principles

- Minimize scope; no frameworks or build pipelines unless requested
- Use Yarn, not npm (`engines.npm`: `please-use-yarn`)
- Match existing Bootstrap 3 grid, modal, and Freelancer class patterns
- See `AGENTS.md` and `README.md` for architecture diagrams and run instructions
